name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Aspect - AI Notes For Interviews & Recruiters

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get custom AI interview summaries for over 30 languages when using Google Meet

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Aspect is your new AI co-pilot for hiring. Human-Level AI Notes for all your interviews. Specifically built for recruiters and busy hiring managers.

Get custom AI interviews summaries for over 30 languages when using Google Meet.

Aspect doesn't just capture and transcribe all your interviews - it understands them. Install the Aspect Chrome extension to create custom notes to your interviews.
